videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets the half-court lob from Grayson Allen and stuffs it in with two hands.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III intercepts a bad pass and finishes on the offensive end with the flush.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley turns defense into offense

videos.description: Bryant Crawford drives right down main street to lay down the emphatic dunk for the Demon Deacons.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Crawford rocks the rim

videos.description: Grayson Allen runs the court and finds a wide-open Alex O'Connell, who drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Duke's Allen displays beautiful court vision

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III dribbles by multiple defenders on his way to an easy slam for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley puts on a show

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets a big block on the defensive end but is hit in the face on his way to the hoop after taking it coast to coast.
videos.headline: Duke's Bagley gets fouled hard
